replies.body:
You have to verify yourself before you can post a thumbnail...
Here is what you do:

1. Go to your dashboard
2. "Channel"
3. Go to "Advanced"
4. If you are not verified you should see a button "Verify"
5. Click that and type in your Phone number
6. You should get a text message with numbers, type them in, in that box.
